==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Wainscoting
<hw>Wain"scot*ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act or
occupation of covering or lining with boards in panel.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The material used to wainscot a house, or the
wainscot as a whole; panelwork.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Wainwright</ent>⟦br⟧
